# AI Coding Instructions for Car Rental System

## Project Rules - READ FIRST ALWAYS

### File Structure (STRICT)
- Components → `src/components/common/` or `src/components/layout/`
- Pages → `src/pages/{PageName}/` with CSS + index.js
- API → `src/services/api/`
- Hooks → `src/hooks/`
- DO NOT create files outside this structure

### Naming (STRICT)
- Components: PascalCase (CarList.jsx)
- Variables: camelCase (carList)
- CSS: kebab-case (.car-list)
- Constants: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE

### Code Standards (ALWAYS)
- Use PropTypes for ALL components
- NO hardcoded API endpoints (use constants)
- ALWAYS try-catch for API calls
- async/await only (no .then)
- Handle errors with user messages

### Component Template
```jsx
import PropTypes from 'prop-types';
import './Name.css';

const Name = ({ prop }) => {
  return <div>{prop}</div>;
};

Name.propTypes = {
  prop: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
};

export default Name;
```

### API Service Pattern
```javascript
import axiosInstance from './axiosConfig';

export const service = {
  get: async () => await axiosInstance.get('/path'),
};
```

### Vietnamese Context
- UI text: Vietnamese
- Date: DD/MM/YYYY
- Currency: VND
- Phone: 10 digits Vietnamese format

### Styling with Tailwind CSS
- Use Tailwind utility classes for ALL styling
- NO separate CSS files for components
- Use responsive prefixes: sm:, md:, lg:, xl:
- Common patterns:
  - Buttons: `px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white rounded-md`
  - Cards: `bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6`
  - Grid: `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6`
  - Flex: `flex justify-between items-center`

### ALWAYS
- Check existing code first
- Reuse utilities
- Follow patterns
- Add comments for complex logic
